It was a very emotional scene at Polokwane Hospital when a stray dog bursts the scene with a dumped baby on its mouth.. The dog is believed to have picked the baby at a nearby dumpsite during its routine food hunting mission. It successfully brought a dumped newly born to the attention of hospital staff who were on their way to a tea break at Polokwane Hospital.RELATED: 7 Signs Of A Toxic Relationship With Your PartnerWith the umbilical cord still attached to the baby, the dog was hailed for successfully delivering the baby unhurt. The hospital staff acknowledged and narrated how the dog approached them but referred all official questions to the PR spokesperson who was unreachable.&nbsp;&nbsp;